QuestData.Title: Rangari Roundup
QuestData.Description: You have a keen eye, $c.$b$bThere are Rangari like myself hidden throughout the Nightmarsh.$b$bI need reports from each of them to ensure the area is safe.$b$bPerhaps you can help me?
QuestData.RewardText: Thank you for the report, $n. We must keep a close eye on these southern wilds.
